        <definition>const double TPM_NI_TASKTIMEOUT</definition>
        <argsstring></argsstring>
        <name>TPM_NI_TASKTIMEOUT</name>
        <initializer>= 0.5</initializer>
        <briefdescription>
<para>After this time in s the background task reading data from the ADC device. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>will not read multiple TP data sets subsequently to keep up if late</para>
<para>it will however still update once per device</para>
<para>so the gui thread can update at least every ~0.5 seconds (default value here)</para>
<para>however the fifo may run full if the timeout is hit too often </para>
        </detaileddescription>
